birth_place.zh-cn: 中华人民共和国福建省福州市
birth_place.en: Fuzhou, Fujian, People's Republic of China

description.zh-cn: 中国共产党中央委员会总书记习近平与妻子彭丽媛的独生女。
description.en: The only daughter of Xi Jinping, General Secretary of the Central Committee of the Communist Party of China, and his wife Peng Liyuan.

description.zh-cn: 中国共产党及中华人民共和国的第五代最高领导人，自2012年起先后担任中共中央总书记、中央军委主席。
description.en: The fifth-generation paramount leader of the Communist Party of China and the People's Republic of China, serving as the General Secretary of the CPC Central Committee and Chairman of the Central Military Commission since 2012.

description.zh-cn: 中华人民共和国国家一级歌唱演员、曾任全国政协委员、解放军艺术学院院长，习近平的妻子。
description.en: A first-class national singer of the People's Republic of China, a former member of the National Committee of the Chinese People's Political Consultative Conference, former president of the PLA Academy of Arts, and the wife of Xi Jinping.

description.zh-cn: 中国共产党、中华人民共和国主要领导人之一，中共八大元老之一，曾任国务院副总理等职务。
description.en: A major leader of the Communist Party of China and the People's Republic of China, one of the Eight Great Elders of the CPC, who served as Vice Premier of the State Council and other positions.

description.zh-cn: 习仲勋的妻子，习近平的母亲。
description.en: Wife of Xi Zhongxun and mother of Xi Jinping.

description.zh-cn: 中华人民共和国福建省的省会，习明泽的出生地。
description.en: The capital city of Fujian Province, People's Republic of China, and the birthplace of Xi Mingze.

description.zh-cn: 习明泽曾就读的幼儿园。
description.en: The kindergarten that Xi Mingze once attended.

description.zh-cn: 习明泽曾就读的小学。
description.en: The primary school that Xi Mingze once attended.

description.zh-cn: 习明泽曾就读的初中及高中。
description.en: The middle and high school that Xi Mingze once attended.

description.zh-cn: 习明泽曾就读的大学。
description.en: The university that Xi Mingze once attended.

description.zh-cn: 习明泽曾就读的美国大学，在此获得文学学士学位并就读研究所。
description.en: The American university that Xi Mingze attended, where she received her Bachelor of Arts degree and later enrolled in graduate studies.

description.zh-cn: 2008年发生于中国四川省的特大地震，习明泽在此期间前往灾区担任志愿者。
description.en: A major earthquake that occurred in Sichuan Province, China in 2008, during which Xi Mingze went to the disaster area as a volunteer.

description.zh-cn: 白俄罗斯总统。
description.en: President of Belarus.

description.zh-cn: 哈佛大学社会科学教授，曾证实习明泽已返回中国。
description.en: A professor of social sciences at Harvard University who once confirmed that Xi Mingze had returned to China.

description.zh-cn: 美国国内的情报与安全机构，据称曾在习明泽留美期间暗中保护她。
description.en: The domestic intelligence and security service of the United States, which allegedly provided covert protection for Xi Mingze during her studies in the US.

description.zh-cn: 美国众议院议员，曾提出法案禁止中共官员及其家人进入美国高等教育系统。
description.en: A member of the U.S. House of Representatives who proposed a bill to ban CCP officials and their families from entering the U.S. higher education system.

description.zh-cn: 中华人民共和国的执政党。
description.en: The founding and sole ruling party of the People's Republic of China.

description.zh-cn: 美国国会的两院之一。
description.en: One of the two chambers of the United States Congress.

en: Eight Elders of the Communist Party of China

description.zh-cn: 指在1980年代至1990年代间，在中华人民共和国拥有实际决策权的一批中国共产党元老，习仲勋是其中之一。
description.en: A group of elderly members of the Communist Party of China who held substantial power in the People's Republic of China during the 1980s and 1990s. Xi Zhongxun was one of them.

description.en: The leading body of the Central Committee of the Communist Party of China.

description.en: The position of Vice Chairperson of the Standing Committee of the National People's Congress.

description.en: The head of the Central Committee of the Communist Party of China and the highest-ranking official within the Communist Party of China.

en: Military Culture College of the National Defence University of the People's Liberation Army

description.zh-cn: 中国人民解放军的一所高等艺术院校，彭丽媛曾任院长。
description.en: A higher arts institution of the People's Liberation Army, where Peng Liyuan once served as the president.

description.zh-cn: 一个信息分享网站，因泄露包括习明泽在内的中国高层公职人员及其家属的个人信息而引发争议。
description.en: An information-sharing website that became controversial for leaking personal information of high-level Chinese public officials and their families, including Xi Mingze.

description.zh-cn: “恶俗维基”案主犯，因泄露习近平女儿习明泽等人的个人信息被重判14年。
description.en: The main person implicated in the 'Esuwiki case', sentenced to 14 years in prison for leaking personal information of individuals including Xi Jinping's daughter, Xi Mingze.

description.zh-cn: 习近平的姐夫，其个人信息在“恶俗维基”案中被泄露。
description.en: Xi Jinping's brother-in-law, whose personal information was leaked in the 'Esuwiki case'.

nodes.id: 反对逃犯条例修订草案运动

zh-cn: 反对逃犯条例修订草案运动

description.zh-cn: 2019年在香港发生的大规模社会运动，“恶俗维基”案相关人员牛腾宇曾前往香港参与。
description.en: A large-scale social movement in Hong Kong in 2019, which Niu Tengyu, a person involved in the 'Esuwiki case', traveled to Hong Kong to participate in.

description.zh-cn: 位于广东省茂名市的法院，审理并判决了“恶俗维基”案。
description.en: The court located in Maoming, Guangdong Province, which tried and sentenced the 'Esuwiki case'.

description.zh-cn: 习近平是习明泽的父亲。
description.en: Xi Jinping is the father of Xi Mingze.

description.zh-cn: 彭丽媛是习明泽的母亲。
description.en: Peng Liyuan is the mother of Xi Mingze.

description.zh-cn: 彭丽媛是习近平的第二任妻子。
description.en: Peng Liyuan is the second wife of Xi Jinping.

description.zh-cn: 习仲勋是习明泽的祖父。
description.en: Xi Zhongxun is the paternal grandfather of Xi Mingze.

description.zh-cn: 齐心是习明泽的祖母。
description.en: Qi Xin is the paternal grandmother of Xi Mingze.

description.zh-cn: 习仲勋是习近平的父亲。
description.en: Xi Zhongxun is the father of Xi Jinping.

description.zh-cn: 齐心是习近平的母亲。
description.en: Qi Xin is the mother of Xi Jinping.

description.zh-cn: 齐心是习仲勋的妻子。
description.en: Qi Xin is the wife of Xi Zhongxun.

description.zh-cn: 为孙女习明泽取名“明泽”，意为“天下开明，泽被苍生”。
description.en: Named his granddaughter Xi Mingze, with 'Mingze' meaning 'to bring enlightenment to the world and benefit all people'.

description.zh-cn: 2010年至2014年于哈佛大学完成本科学业，2019年重新报名研究所学习。
description.en: Completed undergraduate studies at Harvard University from 2010 to 2014, and re-enrolled for graduate studies in 2019.

description.zh-cn: 汶川大地震发生后，时年16岁的习明泽以志愿者的身份前往四川绵竹市的汉旺东汽小学，参与了7天的抢救伤者、心理辅导工作。
description.en: After the Wenchuan earthquake, 16-year-old Xi Mingze went to Hanwang Dongqi Primary School in Mianzhu, Sichuan as a volunteer for 7 days, participating in rescuing the injured and providing psychological counseling.

description.zh-cn: 陪同父母参加为白俄罗斯总统卢卡申科举办的家庭晚宴，这是她首次出席有外国领导人参加的宴会场合。
description.en: Accompanied her parents to a family dinner for Belarusian President Alexander Lukashenko, marking her first appearance at a banquet with a foreign leader.

description.zh-cn: 据称在习明泽于哈佛大学就读期间，美国联邦调查局加派人手对其进行暗中保护。
description.en: It is alleged that during Xi Mingze's studies at Harvard University, the Federal Bureau of Investigation assigned additional personnel to provide her with covert protection.

description.zh-cn: 提出法案，禁止中国共产党党籍官员及其家人进入美国高等教育系统深造。
description.en: Proposed a bill to prohibit officials of the Communist Party of China and their family members from pursuing higher education in the United States.

description.zh-cn: 恶俗维基网站上泄露了习明泽的个人隐私信息，导致相关人员被捕和判刑。
description.en: The Esuwiki website leaked personal information of Xi Mingze, leading to the arrest and sentencing of related individuals.

description.zh-cn: 恶俗维基网站上泄露了邓家贵的个人隐私信息。
description.en: The Esuwiki website leaked personal information of Deng Jiagui.

description.zh-cn: 因在恶俗维基网站上泄露习明泽的个人信息，牛腾宇被判处14年有期徒刑。
description.en: Niu Tengyu was sentenced to 14 years in prison for leaking Xi Mingze's personal information on the Esuwiki website.

relationships.source: 茂名市茂南区人民法院

description.zh-cn: 以“寻衅滋事罪”、“侵犯公民个人信息罪”和“非法经营罪”判处牛腾宇14年有期徒刑及13万元罚款。
description.en: Sentenced Niu Tengyu to 14 years in prison and a fine of 130,000 yuan for 'picking quarrels and provoking trouble', 'infringing on citizens' personal information', and 'illegal business operations'.
